<L>__{exterior interior dry cleaners shop day}
<A>__{sharon is just leaving with a clean uniform on a hanger in a plastic bag. it's a neighborhood place where alterations are done. as she is leaving, an older woman is just entering. this is mrs. vander, beaming at sharon, a real talker.}
